ightSearch|title=Flight Search|website=pegasys.pegast.ru|date=4 September 2018}}</ref> \n<!-- -->\n| [[Sky High Aviation Services|Sky High]] | [[Clayton J. Lloyd International Airport|Anguilla]], [[V. C. Bird International Airport|Antigua]], [[Queen Beatrix International Airport|Aruba]], [[Flamingo International Airport|Bonaire]], [[Hato International Airport|Cura\u00e7ao]], [[Norman Manley International Airport|Kingston]], [[Jose Maria Cordova International Airport|Medellin]], [[Robert L. Bradshaw International Airport|St. Kitts]], [[Princess Juliana International Airport|St. Maarten]], [[Terrance B. Lettsome International Airport|Tortola]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Spirit Airlines]] | [[Fort Lauderdale\u2013Hollywood International Airport|Fort Lauderdale]], [[Newark International Airport|Newark]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Sunrise Airways]] | [[Jos\u00e9 Mart\u00ed International Airport|Havana]], [[Toussaint Louverture International Airport|Port-au-Prince]]<ref>{{cite web |last1=Liu |first1=Jim |title=Sunrise Airways expands Dominican Republic service in 1H20 |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/38/airlineroute/290135/sunrise-airways-expands-dominican-republic-service-in-1h20/ |website=Routesonline |accessdate=6 March 2020}}</ref>\n<!-- -->\n| [[TUI fly Belgium]] | [[Brussels Airport|Brussels]]{{ref|1|5}}\n<!-- -->\n| [[Turpial Airlines]] | [[Arturo Michelena International Airport|Valencia (VE)]] \n<!-- -->\n| [[United Airlines]] | [[Newark Liberty International Airport|Newark]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Venezolana]] | [[Jacinto Lara International Airport|Barquisimeto]], [[Sim\u00f3n Bol\u00edvar International Airport (Venezuela)|Caracas]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Winair]] | [[Princess Juliana International Airport|Sint Maarten]]\n<!-- -->\n| [[Wingo (airline)|Wingo]]  | [[El Dorado International Airport|Bogot\u00e1]]\n}}\n\n;Notes\n*{{note|1|1}} [[Air Cara\u00efbes]]'s flights incoming from Paris-Orly fly via Port-au-Prince, however the return flight from Santo Domingo to Paris-Orly is nonstop.\n*{{note|1|2}} [[Air France]]'s flights incoming from Paris\u2013CDG fly via Punta Cana to Santo Domingo, however the return flight from Santo Domingo to Paris\u2013CDG is nonstop, during the Winter Season, both legs are nonstop.\n*{{note|1|3}} [[Blue Panorama]]'s flights from Milan-Malpensa to Santo Domingo are nonstop, however, the flights from Santo Domingo to Milan-Malpensa are nonstop.\n*{{note|1|4}} [[Condor Flugdienst|Condor]] flies to San Jos\u00e9 via Santo Domingo and has Fifth Freedom Rights to sell tickets between Santo Domingo and San Jos\u00e9. Starting in October, flights to San Jose will stop, therefore the flights from Frankfurt to Santo Domingo will fly via Puerto Plata and nonstop, the flights from Santo Domingo to Frankfurt will all fly nonstop.\n*{{note|1|5}} [[TUI fly Belgium]]'s flights to Brussels fly via Puerto Plata and Punta Cana, however, the flights from Brussels to Santo Domingo are nonstop.\n\n===Cargo===\n{{Airport-dest-list\n|[[Amerijet International]] | [[Luis Munoz Marin International Airport|San Juan]], [[Miami International Airport|Miami]], [[Toussaint Louverture International|Port-Au-Prince]]\n|[[Avianca Cargo]] | [[Bogota Airport|Bogota]], [[Jos\u00e9 Mar\u00eda C\u00f3rdova International Airport|Medellin]]\n|[[UPS Airlines]] | [[Miami International Airport|Miami]], [[Louisville International Airport|Louisville]]\n|[[FedEx]] | [[Miami International Airport|Miami]], [[Memphis International Airport|Memphis]]\n}}\n\n==Statistics==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"font-size: 95%;\"\n|+ '''Top Routes from Las Am\u00e9ricas<br> (2019)'''<ref>[http://www.jac.gob.do/transparencia/index.php/estadisticas/category/521-4to-trimestre {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401200126/http://www.jac.gob.do/transparencia/index.php/estadisticas/category/521-4to-trimestre |date=2019-04-01 }}</ref>\n|-\n! Rank\n! City\n! Passengers\n! Carriers\n|-\n| 1\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[John F. Kennedy International Airport|New York-JFK]]\n| 959,951\